{"tid":388144,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李佳芯與「野獸」男友同居試婚 陳炳銓靠真誠冧掂女神","createTime":"2017-09-05T08:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T10:50:29.000Z","uid":42767,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a2941db5a998447fbbda1ed74bdfb7a47f56632c","tid":388144,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T08:45:22.000Z","msg":"34歲的無線花旦李佳芯去年開始上位，更憑靚樣加演技榮升新一代「宅男女神」，其感情生活亦備受注視，更被踢爆與其貌不揚的ViuTV奀星陳炳銓拍拖，兩人還被網民喻為現代版的「美女與野獸」。雖然有指李佳芯被公司高層「照肺」，惟有轉玩地下情，但隨著女方逐漸坐穩女一之位，她亦冇有怕愈愛愈高調。<br />\n最新一期《東周刊》指李佳芯與男友已發展到於將軍澳同居試婚，近日又甜蜜拍拖到西貢市中心行街，襯晒著白衫情侶裝，為愛巢添置廚具和糧食。另外，陳炳銓接受訪問時承認，與女友相處舒服自然又簡單，自稱沒有特殊魅力，相信是以真誠成功冧掂李佳芯；他又慶幸女友講心唔講金，亦不注重顏值。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170905/_2017090516280784947.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170905%2F_2017090516280784947.jpg&h=3ce17671&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2964d0ebb4fc66332d08f3f1573520a6defa8188","tid":388144,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T08:56:55.000Z","msg":"陳炳銓食唔食煙"},{"pid":"7dbdd818226662cb251052868a58bbc23e23dc42","tid":388144,"uid":3688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T08:59:41.000Z","msg":"Ali<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f78ef857acc35ec05d4a99413d04ccfaa0f7c649","tid":388144,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T09:00:15.000Z","msg":"豬肉佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/